OL,3,CEngland training sessions threatened
OL,4,Cby tornado and storm warnings
OL,6,FA tornado and severe storm threatened
OL,7,Fto disrupt England's first day in
OL,8,FKansas City, hours after police opened
OL,9,Fan investigation into the possible
OL,10,Ftheft of boots and balls from their
OL,11,Ftraining grounds.
OL,13,FThomas Tuchel's side arrived in the
OL,14,FMidwest on Saturday after two days off
OL,15,Fin Florida, and held a community
OL,16,Ftraining session at their Swope Soccer
OL,17,FVillage base at 5pm local time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
