OL,3,CEngland training sessions threatened
OL,4,Cby tornado and storm warnings
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe sun was still searing when the
OL,12,Fsquad first took to the field with
OL,13,Ftemperatures at 30C, but a tornado
OL,14,Fwarning was later put out for parts of
OL,15,Fthe city, with storms due to hit in
OL,16,Fthe early evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
