OL,3,CEngland training sessions threatened
OL,4,Cby tornado and storm warnings
OL,6,FEngland's pre-tournament camp in
OL,7,FFlorida had been littered with weather
OL,8,Fissues, including the side's friendly
OL,9,Fagainst Costa Rica being delayed by an
OL,10,Fhour after a thunderstorm.
OL,12,FThe incoming warning saw Kansas City's
OL,13,Ffan festival - a free event for World
OL,14,FCup supporters to watch the games -
OL,15,Fshut early for safety reasons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
