OL,3,CEngland training sessions threatened
OL,4,Cby tornado and storm warnings
OL,6,FA statement from organisers read: "Due
OL,7,Fto anticipated severe weather, Fifa
OL,8,Ffan festival will be closing early at
OL,9,F5pm and will not reopen today. The
OL,10,Fsafety of the public, staff,
OL,11,Fvolunteers and entertainers remains
OL,12,Four top priority."
OL,14,FThe weather warning comes as police
OL,15,Fconfirmed they were investigating the
OL,16,Ftheft of team equipment before England
OL,17,Farrived at the Kansas City base, after
OL,18,Fballs and boots went missing.
