OL,3,CEngland training sessions threatened
OL,4,Cby tornado and storm warnings
OL,6,FThe Kansas City, Missouri Police
OL,7,FDepartment told the Daily Mail: "We
OL,8,Fare investigating a possible theft of
OL,9,Fequipment from a team vehicle that
OL,10,Farrived in Kansas City with items
OL,11,Fmissing this evening. The
OL,12,Finvestigation is ongoing."
OL,14,FFootball Association sources have
OL,15,Fsince indicated the majority of the
OL,16,Fequipment has now been recovered and
OL,17,Finsisted the incident will not impact
OL,18,Fthe team.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
