OL,3,CEngland training sessions threatened
OL,4,Cby tornado and storm warnings
OL,6,FEngland had received a warm welcome
OL,7,Fwhen they arrived in the city, with
OL,8,Ffans waving to captain Harry Kane and
OL,9,FTuchel as they touched down at the
OL,10,Fhome away from home.
OL,12,FA couple of hundred people greeted
OL,13,Fthem at their Inn at Meadowbrook hotel
OL,14,Fin the south of the city at 1.20pm
OL,15,Flocal time, 7.20pm UK time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
