OL,3,CEngland training sessions threatened
OL,4,Cby tornado and storm warnings
OL,6,FSigns reading 'Good Luck England' with
OL,7,Fa heart featuring the city's initials
OL,8,Fwere dotted along the road to the
OL,9,Fhotel, with 'Welcome' accompanied by
OL,10,Fan image of three lions on the other
OL,11,Fside.
OL,13,FA number of England shirts were
OL,14,Fvisible in the waiting crowd, while
OL,15,FManchester City, Arsenal and Everton
OL,16,Fwere among the clubs represented.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
